name: EHS Code Club
tagline: We are the EHS Code Club!
body:
## About us
The EHS Code Club will allow for students to participate in an open and collaborative OWS-workspace style environment. Allowing for all students and participants to contribute to the Club’s daily functions, administrative duties, etc.


## Our Officers
### President
Max Tuchman is our current President. He can be reached at [fdizile@gmail.com](mailto:fdizile@gmail.com) 

### Vice-President
Cory S. is our current Vice-President.

## Support
Having trouble? Check out our [documentation](https://github.com/EHSCode/docs) and we’ll help you sort it out.
